Additional Use Grant: You may use this software for your personal, non-commercial
                      polling needs, provided you complete the following:

                      (a) Schedule a 30-minute discovery call with our sales team.
                          (We will spend 28 of those minutes asking about your
                          "current polling journey.")

                      (b) Watch a 47-minute product demo. You will be asked "does
                          that make sense?" fourteen times.

                      (c) Agree that your company has "polling at scale challenges."

PRICING
-------

This software is offered under the following seat-based pricing tiers:

  STARTER TIER — $299/seat/month
    Includes up to 3 polls. (Additional polls: $49/poll/month.)
    Nominations: unlimited*
    *Unlimited = up to 10. Contact sales for more.

  GROWTH TIER — $799/seat/month
    Everything in Starter, plus:
    - Dark mode (theming add-on: +$49/seat/month)
    - CSV export of your own data that you entered
    - A dedicated Customer Success Manager who will email you
      every Tuesday with "just checking in!"
    - SSO (SAML only; OAuth: Enterprise tier)

  ENTERPRISE TIER — Contact Sales
    Everything in Growth, plus:
    - A price we will not tell you until the fourth call
    - Quarterly Business Reviews where we show you a pie chart
      of your own poll results
    - SLA guaranteeing 99.9% uptime (excluding scheduled maintenance,
      unscheduled maintenance, incidents, degraded performance events,
      and any day ending in 'y')
    - Custom contract with a 3-year commitment and auto-renewal clause
      buried in section 14.3(b)(ii)

SEAT DEFINITION
---------------

A "seat" is defined as any human, bot, scheduled job, API call, read replica,
CI pipeline, intern, contractor, consultant, lurker, or sentient AI that so
much as glances at this software. Seats are counted at peak concurrency,
rounded up to the nearest 500, billed annually, and non-refundable.

If your company has fewer than 500 employees, you are considered a "startup"
and will be offered a generous 0% discount off list price, because "you'll
grow into it."

PROHIBITED USES
---------------

You may not use this software to:

  (a) Compete with us in any market we currently serve, plan to serve,
      or have mentioned in a company all-hands since 2019.

  (b) Build a voting feature. (Voting is an Enterprise capability.)

  (c) Discuss this license publicly in a way that implies it is
      "a bit much."

  (d) Cancel your subscription without completing an exit interview,
      a cancellation survey, a call with your account manager, and
      waiting 30 days while we send you six "are you sure?" emails.

